sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Browser
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant OAuth as OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant OAuthSrv as OpenShift OAuth Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Backend as Dashboard Backend<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Prom as Prometheus/Thanos<br/>9092/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+

    Note over User,K8sAPI: Flow 1: User Dashboard Access

    User->>Router: HTTPS/443<br/>Initial Request
    Router->>OAuth: HTTPS/8443<br/>Forward Request

    alt User Not Authenticated
        OAuth->>OAuthSrv: HTTPS/6443<br/>OAuth Flow<br/>Redirect for Auth
        OAuthSrv-->>User: Redirect to Login
        User->>OAuthSrv: Login Credentials
        OAuthSrv-->>OAuth: OAuth Token
    end

    OAuth->>Backend: HTTP/8080<br/>Bearer Token in Header
    Backend-->>OAuth: HTML/JS Response
    OAuth-->>Router: HTTPS/8443
    Router-->>User: HTTPS/443<br/>Dashboard UI

    Note over User,K8sAPI: Flow 2: Dashboard API to Kubernetes

    User->>Router: POST /api/notebooks<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>Create Notebook
    Router->>OAuth: HTTPS/8443<br/>Forward Request<br/>Bearer Token
    OAuth->>Backend: HTTP/8080<br/>Validated Request
    Backend->>K8sAPI: HTTPS/6443<br/>POST Notebook CR<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: 201 Created<br/>Notebook Resource
    Backend-->>OAuth: HTTP/8080<br/>JSON Response
    OAuth-->>Router: HTTPS/8443
    Router-->>User: HTTPS/443<br/>Success Response

    Note over User,Prom: Flow 3: Metrics Query

    User->>Router: GET /api/prometheus/query<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>Query Metrics
    Router->>OAuth: HTTPS/8443
    OAuth->>Backend: HTTP/8080<br/>Bearer Token
    Backend->>Prom: HTTPS/9092<br/>Prometheus Query<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Prom-->>Backend: Metrics Data JSON
    Backend-->>OAuth: HTTP/8080
    OAuth-->>Router: HTTPS/8443
    Router-->>User: HTTPS/443<br/>Metrics Response

    Note over User,K8sAPI: Flow 4: WebSocket Communication

    User->>Router: WS Upgrade Request<br/>HTTPS/443
    Router->>OAuth: HTTPS/8443<br/>WebSocket Upgrade
    OAuth->>Backend: WS/8080<br/>Upgrade Connection<br/>Bearer Token
    Backend->>K8sAPI: WSS/6443<br/>Watch Notebook Status<br/>ServiceAccount Token

    loop Real-time Updates
        K8sAPI-->>Backend: Status Update Event
        Backend-->>OAuth: WS/8080
        OAuth-->>Router: HTTPS/8443
        Router-->>User: WS Message<br/>Live Update
    end

    Note over Prom,OAuth: Flow 5: Prometheus Scrape Metrics

    Prom->>OAuth: GET /metrics<br/>HTTPS/8443<br/>No Auth (skip-auth-regex)
    OAuth-->>Prom: Metrics Data<br/>Prometheus Format
